description:
In the times when you need the help and guidance of a trusted attorney, the experienced general civil litigation attorneys at the Orlando-based law firm of Fisher Rushmer, P.A. provides you with the personal attention and respect you both need and desire. Whether you need help through mediation or representation in court, you can expect to have a constant advocate, with a reputation for reliable and comprehensive representation, working for your best interests.

With practice areas including personal injury and wrongful death, insurance and bad faith, motor vehicle accidents, family law, bankruptcy, international law, and medical malpractice, as well as commercial and business litigation addressing issues pertaining to construction law, employment law, real estate law and professional liability, the attorneys at Fisher Rushmer, P.A. handle a variety of cases for both business and personal matters.

At Fisher Rushmer, P.A. customer service is a top priority, which is one reason why you will be served by an attorney, not a case manager, and have access to Spanish bilingual services. Credit cards are accepted and your attorney is available for meetings both on and off-site. You can feel confident that you will receive the aggressive, results-oriented representation you need through the attorneys at Fisher Rushmer, P.A.
